  "readme_html": "<h1 id=\"user-content-a-practical-approach-to-retrieval-augmented-generation-rag-systems\">A Practical Approach to Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) Systems</h1>\n<p>This repository contains the HTML source of <a href=\"https://mallahyari.github.io/rag-ebook/\">A Practical Approach to Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) Systems</a> book. The book is built using <a href=\"https://quarto.org/\">Quarto</a></p>\n<p>If you'd like to support this work, you can buy the pdf version of the book <a href=\"https://angelinamagr.gumroad.com/l/practical-approach-to-RAG-systems\">here</a>.</p>",
